  "2209150": {
    "name": "蛇上而生：序幕 (Above Snakes: Prologue)",
    "steam_appid": 2209150,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于序幕</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209150/extras/fd9c56595c26e227a53764f83cc189e8.poster.avif?t=1762873533\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209150/extras/fd9c56595c26e227a53764f83cc189e8.webm?t=1762873533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209150/extras/fd9c56595c26e227a53764f83cc189e8.mp4?t=1762873533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 《蛇上而生：序幕》中， 你将游玩游戏的开端， 了解游戏的玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >另类的生存体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209150/extras/31d07b041002218f3697c0e8dc45e1f7.poster.avif?t=1762873533\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209150/extras/31d07b041002218f3697c0e8dc45e1f7.webm?t=1762873533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209150/extras/31d07b041002218f3697c0e8dc45e1f7.mp4?t=1762873533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与其他生存游戏不同， 世界并非通过程序生成。 相反， 通过放置等距的世界地块， 靠你自己生成这个世界！ 从伐木工的小定居点“猎者之憩”开始你的旅程， 并围绕着你打造这个世界！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >创造并生存</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209150/extras/22615182c41e0560b0c5f8c30eaa7286.poster.avif?t=1762873533\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209150/extras/22615182c41e0560b0c5f8c30eaa7286.webm?t=1762873533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209150/extras/22615182c41e0560b0c5f8c30eaa7286.mp4?t=1762873533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >确定这个受荒野西部启发的世界景观， 并决定它将如何展现在你面前。 你有权决定下一步做什么。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制作、 烹饪、 狩猎和钓鱼</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209150/extras/acfb0b9d1b5ee98004de0dcfda622c37.poster.avif?t=1762873533\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209150/extras/acfb0b9d1b5ee98004de0dcfda622c37.webm?t=1762873533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209150/extras/acfb0b9d1b5ee98004de0dcfda622c37.mp4?t=1762873533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了帮助猎者之憩的人们， 你可以使用新发现的资源来制作必要的工具。 在皮革加工、 布料编织和其他职业方面取得进步， 为你的冒险创造最好的生存用品！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基地建设</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209150/extras/cf1ea645b0853b96bc461d549a49f852.poster.avif?t=1762873533\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209150/extras/cf1ea645b0853b96bc461d549a49f852.webm?t=1762873533\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2209150/extras/cf1ea645b0853b96bc461d549a49f852.mp4?t=1762873533\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投入资源， 建立自己的小屋， 并建立一个防御和庇护的基地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个身临其境的序幕， 讲述了一个虚构的荒野西部末日事件。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个等距世界， 由玩家在旅程中创造的世界地块所组成。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了生存， 制作、 种植、 狩猎、 钓鱼、 建造基地和战斗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有深度的基地建设系统， 包括广泛的室内和室外资产。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以自己的节奏完成任务， 揭开《蛇上而生》的秘密。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >辅助功能</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整的控制器支持， 按键和按钮重新绑定， 禁用相机摇晃， 禁用平滑相机移动， 光敏感模式， 自定义音效、 音乐、 进食噪音和脚步声的音量控制。</p>",
